      "Dentistry is her passion, and she enjoys empowering people to keep a healthy mouth. She strives to help every patient have a positive experience and feel at ease at the dentist. She empathizes with those who have dental anxiety and is more than willing to work with you to find the most comfortable way through your care. Detail-oriented by nature, she focuses on precision and strives for excellence in all her restorative work.",
