    paras: [
      "Juliana is excited to be part of the Centennial team. Originally from Florida, she received her Bachelor of Science in Biology from Nova Southeastern University, then graduated from Indian River State College in 2013 with a degree in Dental Hygiene. She moved to Washington right after graduation and now calls the state home. She is passionate about gentle, personalized care and patient education. Outside of work, she loves spending time with her husband and their two kids, and in a spare moment you’ll find her with a good book or a movie.",
