    paras: [
      "Ciara, a scheduling coordinator, joined the team in 2024, bringing 6 years of scheduling and insurance-billing expertise. She loves when a patient can leave smiling with all the information they need. A Washington native who grew up in Lake Stevens, she’s usually either in another country or at a country music concert when she’s not in the office.",
